tent><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24248182/amazon-october-prime-day-best-early-deals-echo-speakers-displays-fire-tablets-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24248182/amazon-october-prime-day-best-early-deals-echo-speakers-displays-fire-tablets-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry></feed>